urlText: Wynyard Lift Outage between George Street and Concourse
content:
Customers, due to Wynyard station upgrade the lifts from George Street to Concourse Level will be closed from Saturday 08 February until July 2020.

During these works, Customers will be ableuse alternate lifts from Wynyard Station to Carrington Street and York Street accessed via Margaret Street.

For further information or assistance, Please follow station staff instructions, station signage or call Wynyard Station on 9224 2959.
subtitle: Wynyard Lift Outage between George Street and Concourse

urlText: Central Station: Southern tunnel temporarily closed
content:
From 10pm to 5am each night starting Monday 17 through to Thursday 20 February, the Southern Tunnel at Central Station will be temporarily closed due to Sydney Metro works.

To access Platforms 4 - 23 please follow signs and use the Suburban Tunnel or the Northern Concourse.
subtitle: Central Station: Southern tunnel temporarily closed
